Dorn in NRO, when hailed by an evil race, will ask if you are there on business or seek shelter. Tell him you are on business. He says, who sent you? You tell him Zimbittle sent me. He says that he does not believe you and asks for the password. The password is Mukk. He then gives you a note to take to Kragia of Da'Bashers in Grobb. He also says that thenote must not fall into the hands of Goonda or the whole plan would get disrupted. The note can be read and tells of a plan to invade the ogre encampment, where a traitor will take the crystal shard and return it to Neriak. If you give the note to Kragia, he DOES NOT respond with the normal &quot;umm.. Tanks&quot; but says something like &quot;I don't know what dis for.. but I keep it&quot;. My guess is that he cannot read. <BR>
Now, I am guessing that this is related to the spawning of the DE female in WK. Being I am a troll warrior I cannot gate there and find out. Another guess is that when she spawns, you will need to prevent the ogres from killing her (don't even know for sure if they would) and watch for her to take some action or even hail her and see what she says.<BR>
I really hope that this goes somewhere...<BR>
<BR>
Zen
